#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_stairs/api.lua:185
msgid ""
"Stairs are useful to reach higher places by walking over them; jumping is "
"not required. Placing stairs in a corner pattern will create corner stairs. "
"Stairs placed on the ceiling or at the upper half of the side of a block "
"will be placed upside down."
msgstr ""
"Eskailerak leku altuagoetara iristeko erabilgarriak dira haien gainean "
"ibiltzean; Ez da beharrezkoa salto egitea. Izkina batean eskailerak jartzeak "
"izkinako eskailerak sortuko ditu. Bloke baten aldeko sabaian edo goiko "
"erdian jarritako eskailerak ahuspez jarriko dira."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_stairs/api.lua:314 mods/ITEMS/mcl_stairs/api.lua:529
msgid "Double @1"
msgstr "@1 Bikoitza"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_stairs/api.lua:315
msgid ""
"Slabs are half as high as their full block counterparts and occupy either "
"the lower or upper part of a block, depending on how it was placed. Slabs "
"can be easily stepped on without needing to jump. When a slab is placed on "
"another slab of the same type, a double slab is created."
msgstr ""
"Lauzak bloke osoko kontraparteen altueren erdiak dira, eta bloke baten "
"behealdea edo goikaldea hartzen dute, jarri den moduaren arabera. Lauzak "
"erraz zapaldu daitezke, jauzi egin beharrik gabe. Lauza bat mota bereko "
"beste lauza batean jartzen denean, lauza bikoitza sortzen da."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_stairs/api.lua:402
msgid "Upper @1"
msgstr "Goiko @1"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_stairs/api.lua:438
msgid ""
"Double slabs are full blocks which are created by placing two slabs of the "
"same kind on each other."
msgstr ""
"Lauza bikoitzak bloke osoak dira, eta mota bereko bi lauza elkarren gainean "
"jarriz sortzen dira."
